experience.description:
- Lead Engagement: Respond promptly to inbound inquiries from potential customers via email, phone, and LinkedIn;
- Assess the needs of inbound leads by asking the right questions to identify their challenges, goals, and fit for our solutions;
- Collaborate with Account Executives by scheduling product demos and ensuring a seamless handoff of qualified leads;
- Accurately record lead details and interactions in the CRM system to maintain a clean and organized sales pipeline;
- Initiate contact with prospects via email, cold calls, and LinkedIn to introduce our solutions and qualify their needs.

- Regularly communicated with clients via phone and in-person meetings to provide updates and address inquiries regarding ongoing projects;
- Account management of current clients, resulting in 70% increase in client satisfaction and 15% growth in account revenue;
- Conducted regular check-ins with clients to understand their needs, resolve issues, and identify opportunities for upselling or cross-selling additional services;
- Respond promptly to inbound inquiries from potential customers via phone or email;
- Development of work plans and operational strategies;
- Implementation of a new framework to track work hours that increased significantly operational efficiency;
- Assisting in successful delivery by maintaining detailed project documentation and reports;
- Developed a track system for budget, returns of material, receipts, and expenses.

- Immersed to a different culture, developing daily competences and skills to adapt to the new environment;
- Improved English proficiency, becoming a fluent speaker;
- Willed to study and work during the exchange program;
- Detail oriented to the tasks received;
- Effectively coordinated activities and projects with children, promoting cultural experiences from both parts;
- Time management and problem-solving skills dealing with children in some adversity situations.

- Developed product marketing strategies, including branding and new products in the market;
- Advertisement writing and copywriting articles to the company website;
- Utilized market analysis and SEO techniques, using Google Analytics and Google Ads to promote and analyze data for the development of more effective marketing strategies. As a case in point, one account started from zero and grew by 16% in one week on Google Ads.

- Experience in Customer Success (or Customer Experience) in a startup;
- Created an onboarding content strategy by reducing time on a phone call with the customer, from 30 minutes to 0;
- Initiated the implementation of a Customer Relationship Management (CRM);
- Strategically separate the target groups for better performance on the content;
- Customer journey mapping; 
- Customer advocacy to ensure customer satisfaction and loyalty;
- Developed strategic content tailored to various target groups;
- Collecting and analyzing customer feedback;
- Designed content strategy and proactively identified opportunities to develop new schemes and plans.
